flowchart TD
    A[Guest opens system] --> B{Has account?}
    B -->|No| C[register.php]
    C --> D[Validate school/course/mobile/email/password]
    D --> E{Valid and unique?}
    E -->|No| C
    E -->|Yes| F[Create OTP session register_account]
    F --> G[Send OTP via SMS]
    G --> H[register-otp.php]
    H --> I{OTP verified?}
    I -->|No| H
    I -->|Yes| J[Create users row role=applicant status=active]
    J --> K[Login redirect]

    B -->|Yes| L[login.php]
    L --> M[Find user by mobile]
    M --> N{Password correct and account active?}
    N -->|No| L
    N -->|Yes| O[Create authenticated session]
    O --> P{Role}
    P -->|applicant| Q[dashboard.php]
    P -->|admin/staff| R[index.php admin or shared modules]

    Q --> S[Optional: resume draft application wizard]
    Q --> T[my-application.php status tracking]
    Q --> U[notifications.php]
    Q --> V[profile-settings.php / account-security.php]

    V --> W[Request OTP for mobile change]
    W --> X{OTP verified?}
    X -->|No| V
    X -->|Yes| Y[Update mobile in users]

    L --> Z[forgot-password.php]
    Z --> AA[Request OTP by mobile]
    AA --> AB{OTP + new password valid?}
    AB -->|No| Z
    AB -->|Yes| AC[Update users.password_hash]
